      *****************************************************************
       320-BODY-HEN-SEC      SECTION.
      *
           INITIALIZE          SUM-AREA
           MOVE    KEY-NEW     TO   KEY-OLD 
      *
           PERFORM  VARYING    IDX1  FROM  1  BY  1
                    UNTIL      IDX1  >    10
                    OR         KEY-NEW  NOT    =   KEY-OLD
                    OR         FLG-PRINT       =   1
      *
      *    診療年月
             MOVE    MF100-SRYYM         TO  WRK-SYMD (1:6)
             MOVE    "01"                TO  WRK-SYMD (7:2)
             PERFORM 31012-SEIWA-HEN-SEC
             MOVE    WRK-HENYMDG(5:4)    TO  SC03-SRYYM(IDX1)(1:4)
             MOVE    WRK-HENYMDG(11:4)   TO  SC03-SRYYM(IDX1)(5:4)
      *
      *    受給者番号
             MOVE    MF100-JKYSNUM       TO  SC03-JKYSNUM(IDX1)
      *
      *    乳幼児氏名
             MOVE    MF100-NAME          TO  SC03-NAME(IDX1)
      *
      *    保険者番号
             MOVE    MF100-HKNJANUM      TO  SC03-HKNJANUM(IDX1)
      *
      *    記号・番号
             MOVE    MF100-KIGO          TO  SC03-KIGO(IDX1)
             MOVE    MF100-NUM           TO  SC03-NUM(IDX1)
      *
      *    レセプト種別
      *      高額療養費か
             IF  MF100-KOGAKU  =  1
               MOVE  "○"                TO  SC03-KOGAKU (IDX1)
             ELSE
               IF      MF100-NYUGAIKBN     =   "1"
                 IF    MF100-KYURATE       =   30
                   MOVE  "○"            TO  SC03-FTNRATE(IDX1 3)
                 ELSE
                   MOVE  "○"            TO  SC03-FTNRATE(IDX1 4)
                 END-IF
               ELSE
                 IF    MF100-KYURATE       =   30
                   MOVE  "○"            TO  SC03-FTNRATE(IDX1 1)
                 ELSE
                   MOVE  "○"            TO  SC03-FTNRATE(IDX1 2)
                 END-IF
               END-IF
             END-IF
      *
      *    初診回数
             MOVE  MF100-SYOSIN          TO  WRK-Z2
             MOVE  WRK-Z2                TO  SC03-KAISU(IDX1)
      * 
      *    一部負担金
             MOVE  MF100-FTNMONEY        TO  WRK-Z6
             MOVE  WRK-Z6                TO  SC03-ITBFTN(IDX1)
      *
      *    入院日数
             IF    MF100-NYUGAIKBN       =   "1"
               MOVE  MF100-JNISSU        TO  WRK-Z2
               MOVE  WRK-Z2              TO  SC03-NISSU(IDX1)
             END-IF
      *
      *    診療点数
             MOVE    MF100-TOTALTEN      TO  WRK-Z7
             MOVE    WRK-Z7              TO  SC03-TENSU(IDX1)
      *
      *    高額療養費限度額
             MOVE    MF100-KOGAKUTEN     TO  WRK-Z7
             MOVE    WRK-Z7              TO  SC03-KOGAKUTEN(IDX1)
      *
      *    小計加算
             ADD     MF100-SYOSIN        TO  SUM-GSYOSIN
             ADD     MF100-FTNMONEY      TO  SUM-GITBFTN
             ADD     MF100-TOTALTEN      TO  SUM-GTENSU
             ADD     MF100-KOGAKUTEN     TO  SUM-GKOGAKUTEN
      *
             PERFORM   900-TMP-READ-SEC
           END-PERFORM
      *
      *    小計編集
