           MOVE    WRK-Z3                TO  SC03-GKAISU
           MOVE    SUM-GITBFTN           TO  WRK-Z9
           MOVE    WRK-Z9                TO  SC03-GITBFTN
           MOVE    SUM-GTENSU            TO  WRK-Z9
           MOVE    WRK-Z9                TO  SC03-GTENSU
           MOVE    SUM-GKOGAKUTEN        TO  WRK-Z9
           MOVE    WRK-Z9                TO  SC03-GKOGAKUTEN
